/// cairo_line_join_t:
/// @CAIRO_LINE_JOIN_MITER: use a sharp (angled) corner, see
/// cairo_set_miter_limit() (Since 1.0)
/// @CAIRO_LINE_JOIN_ROUND: use a rounded join, the center of the circle is the
/// joint point (Since 1.0)
